snippet.title: Space Impact: Kappa Base for Nokia N-Gage (Next Gen / 2.0)
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay video of Space Impact: Kappa Base, a first party shoot-em-up for the new N-Gage phone gaming platform.

At the moment the N-Gage platform is available on the Nokia 5320 XpressMusic, N81, N81 8GB, N82, N95 and N95 8GB, but many more phones will be added to the list over time.

For more news, reviews and info about the new N-Gage platform, visit www.allaboutngage.com
